ay |publisher=[[National Research Institute for Cultural Properties, Tokyo]] |accessdate=19 May 2011}}</ref> A cannon and a drum have been designated as {{ill|Cultural Property (Japan)|en|Cultural Property (Japan)|WD=Q858308|lt=Cultural Properties|1=Cultural Property (Japan)}} by the city.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.city.mito.lg.jp/view.rbz?nd=1379&of=1&ik=1&pnp=1373&pnp=1374&pnp=1379&cd=1479 |title=Mito bunkazai |publisher=[[Mito, Ibaraki|Mito City]] |accessdate=19 May 2011}}</ref>

